Pre-requisite of PCA:

  • It assumes the relationship between variables in the dataset is linear
  • We need to scale data before using PCA as its sensitive to this
  • PCA works better if there is more variance in the data

Advantages of PCA :

  • It helps to reduce dimentionality of the data
  • Helps to extract important features
  • Noise Reduction

Disadvantages of PCA:

  • Its not easy to understand the principal components every time
  • Information loss
